#### Requirements ####

- opensync >= 0.32
- glib-2.0
- libxml-2.0
- libxslt
- sync4j SDK 6.0.8


#### Installation ####

The sync4j SDK can be found in the sync4j-SDK folder.
1) Extract the archive and apply the patch:
$ unzip funambol-cpp-api-6.0.8.zip
$ cd Funambol/
$ patch -p0 < ../sync4j-6.0.8.patch

2) Configure, build and install
$ cd sdk/c++/build/autotools/
$ chmod u+x autogen.sh
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure --enable-xmlconfig=yes
$ make
$ make install

Then configure, build and install the plugin
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure 
$ make
$ make install


